rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0010
rows.name: Can't believe how much you got up and running.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0020
rows.name:
I know I was M.I.A. for a good long while,
but it's not like you've had years.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0030
rows.name: Honestly, I'm impressed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0040
rows.name: It's growing on me, this NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0050
rows.name: Good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0060
rows.name: Mind letting go of that grudge already, Princess?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0070
rows.name: I don't know what you're talking about.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0080
rows.name: What exactly is there for me to hold a grudge over?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0090
rows.name: Well, since I left you alone for all this time...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0100
rows.name: Figured you were sour about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0110
rows.name: Let's see.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0120
rows.name: If only you'd stayed behind with me...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0130
rows.name: I could've had it a whole lot easier than I did.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0140
rows.name:
Maybe it's obvious,
since you came to us from the Air Force,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0150
rows.name: but your piloting skills were a cut above.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0160
rows.name:
Anyone could see your promotion would be
just a matter of time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0170
rows.name: So when you left the team so soon after joining...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0190
rows.name: I was happy for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0200
rows.name: So if there was one thing I'm "sour" about...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0210
rows.name:
it's that I made you take the Ares.
...I'm angry at myself for that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0220
rows.name: When we were leaving Earth...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0230
rows.name: I prioritized directing my team.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0240
rows.name: So when you took the Ares,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0250
rows.name:
and dove into the heart of the enemy swarm,
I couldn't do much to stop you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0260
rows.name: A mistake.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0270
rows.name: I depended on your skills too much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0280
rows.name: And so they crowned you a hero,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0290
rows.name: made you the Ares's sole pilot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0300
rows.name: And you kept on protecting us,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0310
rows.name:
until the day of the battle that ended with us
crashing down on Mira, and you...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0320
rows.name: gone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0330
rows.name: How I regretted it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0340
rows.name: Forcing the Ares on you,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0350
rows.name:
the way that I drove you into taking up
the hero's mantle...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0360
rows.name: So much guilt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0370
rows.name: You didn't do that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0380
rows.name: I went charging off on my own.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0390
rows.name:
I was like a kid with a new toy,
though I should've known better.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0400
rows.name: Nah, I'm no hero.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0410
rows.name: I was just...terrified.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0420
rows.name: Scared that I'd lose my place in the world,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0425
rows.name: just like I lost my motherland when I was a kid.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0430
rows.name: I needed the White Whale intact.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0440
rows.name: The Ares was just a means to that end.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0450
rows.name: A means, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0460
rows.name: You know,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0470
rows.name: I'm the same as you then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0480
rows.name: I lost the planet where I was born,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0485
rows.name:
and came to Earth with the Ares
an unwilling companion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0490
rows.name: But I think,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0500
rows.name: that's giving the thing far too little credit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0510
rows.name: The Ares wasn't just a toolâ€”[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0520
rows.name: This Skell was always leading the way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0530
rows.name: Guiding us...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0540
rows.name: where we're needed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0550
rows.name: "Needed"?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0560
rows.name: Here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0570
rows.name: Yes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0580
rows.name: ...I'm glad you came back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31140100_MSG0590
rows.name: Truly.[ST:wait ]
